Dialogue: 99,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:00:13.99,0:00:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what you'll be\Nuntil you've grown up.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is it the same for witches?
Dialogue: 99,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps]
Dialogue: 99,0:00:45.56,0:00:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco sighs]
Dialogue: 99,0:00:47.48,0:00:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[wind blowing]
Dialogue: 99,0:00:52.24,0:00:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco exclaims]
Dialogue: 99,0:01:19.14,0:01:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs tiredly]
Dialogue: 99,0:01:21.06,0:01:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'm making\Na big mess, aren't I?
Dialogue: 99,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm almost done.
Dialogue: 99,0:01:28.69,0:01:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry,\Nit'll go back to normal.
Dialogue: 99,0:01:31.15,0:01:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This spring is touched\Nby magic!
Dialogue: 99,0:01:58.47,0:02:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never get tired of it.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:00.68,0:02:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic is so... amazing!
Dialogue: 99,0:02:07.10,0:02:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The world around us\Nis brimming with magic.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:10.52,0:02:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A blessing that improves\Nour lives in so many ways.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:14.98,0:02:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But how it works\Nis a bit of a mystery.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:18.74,0:02:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The only ones who can\Ncast spells are witches.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:22.28,0:02:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[cattle bleating]
Dialogue: 99,0:02:23.87,0:02:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] All we ordinary people\Ncan do is sit back
Dialogue: 99,0:02:27.29,0:02:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and enjoy the results.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:29.54,0:02:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can never use\Nmagic ourselves.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:34.67,0:02:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had been born a witch.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:40.43,0:02:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 99,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sheets of white,
Dialogue: 99,0:02:47.18,0:02:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,become now a cloak of flight!
Dialogue: 99,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 99,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] No, come back!
Dialogue: 99,0:02:57.19,0:02:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the kind\Nof flight I meant!
Dialogue: 99,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:03:08.08,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[exclaims softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco panting]
Dialogue: 99,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A Pegasus Carriage!
Dialogue: 99,0:03:18.80,0:03:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[exclaims excitedly]
Dialogue: 99,0:03:30.64,0:03:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen one land!\NI can't wait!
Dialogue: 99,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, look!
Dialogue: 99,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a Pegasus Carriage!
Dialogue: 99,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 99,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, where are you?
Dialogue: 99,0:03:44.45,0:03:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 99,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 99,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH] Huh?
Dialogue: 99,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] Hm.
Dialogue: 99,0:03:52.46,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, sir!\NI didn't know you were there.
Dialogue: 99,0:03:54.71,0:03:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite all right.
Dialogue: 99,0:03:56.25,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my own fault.\NA poor place to stand.
Dialogue: 99,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN 1]\NMy word, I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine, finding such a garment\Nall the way out here!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:03.30,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN 2] Ah, yes, but isn't\Nwood-sorrel embroidery
Dialogue: 99,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,a tad dated?
Dialogue: 99,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look at this!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Genuine Harrian lace!\N- [both gasp]
Dialogue: 99,0:04:10.81,0:04:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN 2] Amazing! The stock\Nin the castle town
Dialogue: 99,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- sold out almost immediately.\N- [Coco exclaims]
Dialogue: 99,0:04:15.23,0:04:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- [indistinct chatter]\N- It must have been them!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:16.69,0:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They came\Nin the Pegasus Carriage!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- [women chuckle]\N- Oh. No, I'm not with them.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:22.24,0:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, but do you perhaps\Nhave any more lace like this?
Dialogue: 99,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO'S MOM]\NOh, of course, ma'am.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right with you!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco? I could use your help!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN 3] How about this one?
Dialogue: 99,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we do for you, sir?
Dialogue: 99,0:04:33.71,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for some\Nsmoke-colored fabric.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can come again.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I could cut it for you\Nif you like!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you, now?
Dialogue: 99,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in good hands with her!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- I see.\N- [indistinct chatter continues]
Dialogue: 99,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps excitedly]\NWhen I'm done,
Dialogue: 99,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,can I go see\Nthe Pegasus Carriage?
Dialogue: 99,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Go see the what?
Dialogue: 99,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a Pegasus Carriage\Noutside!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for goodness' sake.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:54.44,0:04:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We've talked about this.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No meddling\Nwith the customers' property.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] I'll only look,\NI promise!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco's mom sighs]
Dialogue: 99,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] I'll stop talking about
Dialogue: 99,0:05:02.61,0:05:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,how I want to be a witch\Nall the time. Please?
Dialogue: 99,0:05:05.91,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO'S MOM] Mm...
Dialogue: 99,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- [indistinct chatter continues]\N- [Coco's mom sighs]
Dialogue: 99,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, fine, but\Nonly after you've finished.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps excitedly] Thank you.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:14.21,0:05:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!\NWhat measurements did you need?
Dialogue: 99,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- [QIFREY] Oh, here they are.\N- I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[inhales, blows softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 99,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Uh?
Dialogue: 99,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco whimpers]
Dialogue: 99,0:05:59.67,0:06:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 99,0:06:01.34,0:06:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have excellent focus\Nand steady hands.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:05.63,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No hesitation in the line.\NClean cut.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:08.76,0:06:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And a finish showing\Nprecision and care.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea\Nthis village possessed
Dialogue: 99,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,such a skilled artisan.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is real magic.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:06:20.19,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[shrieks] No! What I do here\Nisn't anything like magic!
Dialogue: 99,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic is mysterious,\Nand priceless,
Dialogue: 99,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and wonderfully shiny\Nand sparkly,
Dialogue: 99,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and unbelievably beautiful!
Dialogue: 99,0:06:29.99,0:06:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just so... so precious,
Dialogue: 99,0:06:34.08,0:06:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,more precious than I can say.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:36.41,0:06:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, come to think of it,\Nwhat am I saying?
Dialogue: 99,0:06:39.58,0:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting the sense\Nyou truly love magic.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that? Tell me.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:47.42,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco sighs]
Dialogue: 99,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] When I was little,\Nmy mother took me
Dialogue: 99,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to a festival at the castle.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And while I was there,
Dialogue: 99,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I met a witch wearing a mask.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[♪ mysterious music playing]
Dialogue: 99,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[WITCH] You there, child.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to buy\Na magic picture book?
Dialogue: 99,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic?
Dialogue: 99,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I love picture books,
Dialogue: 99,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never heard of magic.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:31.43,0:07:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[WITCH] Why, magic is a miracle\Nthat makes this world vibrant.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:36.43,0:07:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A Pegasus Carriage in the sky,
Dialogue: 99,0:07:39.14,0:07:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a spring with waters\Never crystal clear.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:42.44,0:07:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the cobblestones underfoot,
Dialogue: 99,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,glowing brightly with each step.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:47.94,0:07:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these things are magic.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps delightedly]
Dialogue: 99,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 99,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, magic is the best!
Dialogue: 99,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I love magic!
Dialogue: 99,0:07:58.66,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[WITCH] Buy the book\Nand get this wand for free.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:01.33,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:08:04.79,0:08:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's what you spent\Nthe money on?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:07.55,0:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you wanted to get\Nsome roasted strawberries.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:10.63,0:08:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I did! But then\NI followed a butterfly,
Dialogue: 99,0:08:12.93,0:08:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and I found a person\Nwearing a pointed hat!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, so you told me\Nonce already.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:17.47,0:08:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, I have\Na magic picture book!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And a wand too!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:21.60,0:08:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco's mom chuckles]
Dialogue: 99,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then.\NIt's getting late, Coco,
Dialogue: 99,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we should start heading home.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- [COCO] Mommy!\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When I grow up,
Dialogue: 99,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to become a witch\Nand use my magic
Dialogue: 99,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to make the whole world vibrant,\Njust you wait!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:36.49,0:08:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But why not?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:38.37,0:08:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, you can't simply decide\Nto become a witch and use magic.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:42.83,0:08:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a power\Nyou have to be born with.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it's not\Nsomething ordinary people
Dialogue: 99,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,are capable of.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:51.34,0:08:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you're ready,\Nlet's go home.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:53.55,0:08:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But look! The ground shines\Nwherever I step!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:57.39,0:08:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO'S MOM] Uh...
Dialogue: 99,0:08:58.39,0:09:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[both chuckle]
Dialogue: 99,0:09:00.51,0:09:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO'S MOM] Well, let's see\Nif it keeps on shining
Dialogue: 99,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,all the way home.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:05.14,0:09:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, maybe\Nyou can use magic.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco exclaims softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:09:17.53,0:09:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since, it's been my dream\Nto become a witch,
Dialogue: 99,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't seem to let it go.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be interested in hearing\Na bit more about the...
Dialogue: 99,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[loud thud]
Dialogue: 99,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- [WOMAN 3] Oh, my...\N- [WOMAN 2] What was that?
Dialogue: 99,0:09:28.83,0:09:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO'S MOM] Coco?
Dialogue: 99,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- [MAN] Whoa there, settle down.\N- [horses neighing]
Dialogue: 99,0:09:32.71,0:09:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Steady. Steady!
Dialogue: 99,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasp]
Dialogue: 99,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[cattle bleating]
Dialogue: 99,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, now look what you did.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[TANERL] Shut up. Ow...
Dialogue: 99,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Are you all right?
Dialogue: 99,0:09:49.73,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Coco.\N- [COCO] What happened?
Dialogue: 99,0:09:51.40,0:09:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't do anything.\NIt just suddenly fell apart.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it didn't, liar!
Dialogue: 99,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It fell because you crawled\Nunderneath it!
Dialogue: 99,0:09:57.45,0:09:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[TANERL] You snitch!
Dialogue: 99,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He hit his head\Nwhile he was down there.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And it fell over.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN 3]\NNo! This is absolutely terrible!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- [gasping]\N- What have you done
Dialogue: 99,0:10:04.79,0:10:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to our Pegasus Carriage?
Dialogue: 99,0:10:05.91,0:10:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN 2]\NIt belongs to my father!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:08.21,0:10:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We are so sorry!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure these boys feel awful\Nfor troubling you.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How does your apology help us?
Dialogue: 99,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a carriage,\Nwe can't return home!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO'S MOM]\NOh, dear me, what can we do?
Dialogue: 99,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] Pardon me.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I could be of service.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:25.31,0:10:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I took a look,
Dialogue: 99,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and the damage doesn't appear\Nto be serious.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? And who are you?
Dialogue: 99,0:10:31.06,0:10:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies, allow me\Nto cap off my attire.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:36.49,0:10:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:10:40.87,0:10:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Qifrey the witch,\Nat your service, madam.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH] A pointed hat.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can fix it, then?
Dialogue: 99,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] Indeed.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN] You certainly are\Na lifesaver, Sir Witch!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:54.71,0:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY]\NIt's nothing at all.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, I'll simply need to reapply\Nthe spell
Dialogue: 99,0:10:57.92,0:10:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to the floorboard\Nof the carriage.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your help is appreciated!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And happily given!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:03.22,0:11:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this work\Nenvironment is a bit...
Dialogue: 99,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use our workshop,\Nwe would be
Dialogue: 99,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- so honored and delighted!\N- Coco!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:08.18,0:11:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What? We would, Mom,\Nwouldn't we?
Dialogue: 99,0:11:12.15,0:11:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he's an honest\Nto goodness witch.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:17.23,0:11:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be the chance\NI've been waiting for,
Dialogue: 99,0:11:19.99,0:11:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to witness the very moment\Na spell is cast!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:27.75,0:11:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[cattle bleating]
Dialogue: 99,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask for your assistance?
Dialogue: 99,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I will need someone\Nto keep watch,
Dialogue: 99,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can cast\Nthe spell in private.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:38.01,0:11:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No one must come in\Nunder any circumstances.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:41.38,0:11:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it was too much\Nto hope for.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:48.60,0:11:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, why can't we see\Nhow it's done?
Dialogue: 99,0:11:52.56,0:11:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic is practiced\Nall over the world,
Dialogue: 99,0:11:55.69,0:11:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,yet most of us don't have\Nthe first clue how it happens.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:58.98,0:12:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Only witches know the secret.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret... Oh?
Dialogue: 99,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- [COCO] Where'd they go?\N- [TANERL] Almost fell!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:13.58,0:12:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] What do you two think\Nyou're doing?
Dialogue: 99,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAMLA] She caught us!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[TANERL] She doesn't matter.\NWe're fine.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we see into the room\Nfrom here?
Dialogue: 99,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- [COCO] Wait for me!\N- Fine, but keep your voice down!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Out of the way!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[all exclaim]
Dialogue: 99,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, talk about disappointing.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What a letdown.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[wind howling]
Dialogue: 99,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco whimpers] What is this?
Dialogue: 99,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[wind howling]
Dialogue: 99,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] I shouldn't!
Dialogue: 99,0:13:23.78,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really want to!\NBut I shouldn't!
Dialogue: 99,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] He's drawing.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Drawing magic?
Dialogue: 99,0:14:02.69,0:14:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,With a pen?
Dialogue: 99,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The wand that I got that day.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it actually...
Dialogue: 99,0:14:11.03,0:14:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:13.33,0:14:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Witches don't cast spells.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They draw them!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] That's that.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco, all finished here.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco panting]
Dialogue: 99,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco?
Dialogue: 99,0:14:32.55,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Oh, are you done?\N[panting]
Dialogue: 99,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[horses neighing]
Dialogue: 99,0:14:44.36,0:14:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[bird squawking]
Dialogue: 99,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco's mom sighs]
Dialogue: 99,0:14:51.78,0:14:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I was starting\Nto worry there for a moment.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Uh?
Dialogue: 99,0:14:55.79,0:14:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO'S MOM]\NWell, you're in love with magic.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:58.71,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been ever since\Nyou were little.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought you might ask\Nto leave home
Dialogue: 99,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- and go off with that witch.\N- [Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:15:06.21,0:15:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO'S MOM] I already lost\Nyour father to illness.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:08.42,0:15:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to face\Nlosing you too,
Dialogue: 99,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I'd do.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:12.93,0:15:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You never will, Mom!
Dialogue: 99,0:15:14.47,0:15:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I won't ever\Nleave you all alone!
Dialogue: 99,0:15:20.06,0:15:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO'S MOM] My goodness,\Naren't you a sweet girl.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO'S MOM] Hm?
Dialogue: 99,0:15:31.61,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mm... [chuckles]\N- [giggles]
Dialogue: 99,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[both sigh]
Dialogue: 99,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight, Mom.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO'S MOM] Goodnight, dear.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, Coco?\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 99,0:15:49.47,0:15:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet dreams.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco sighs softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:16:02.64,0:16:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might ask\Nto leave home
Dialogue: 99,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and go off with that witch.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco sighs]
Dialogue: 99,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] The patterns\Nin the picture book,
Dialogue: 99,0:16:26.84,0:16:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the free wand\Nthat came with it...
Dialogue: 99,0:16:30.55,0:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They were more than\Nthey seemed.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a magic pen!
Dialogue: 99,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[creaking]
Dialogue: 99,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Forgive me, Mom.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go anywhere, but...
Dialogue: 99,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to try it!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[pen scratching]
Dialogue: 99,0:17:23.10,0:17:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco breathes shakily]
Dialogue: 99,0:17:41.33,0:17:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[soft jingling]
Dialogue: 99,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Huh?
Dialogue: 99,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans] Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 99,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of course it wouldn't be\Nthat easy.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:53.05,0:17:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:18:05.23,0:18:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[exclaims]
Dialogue: 99,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[exclaims]
Dialogue: 99,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] It sparkled!\NThat must mean it worked!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!\NI used magic!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:23.08,0:18:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I used actual,\Nreal-life magic! [squealing]
Dialogue: 99,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So magic is drawn.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't supposed\Nto see it!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:29.58,0:18:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I get into trouble\Nif he finds out?
Dialogue: 99,0:18:36.80,0:18:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll draw...
Dialogue: 99,0:18:38.97,0:18:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,just one more.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:41.09,0:18:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:18:53.52,0:18:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] A picture book.\NHow curious.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it nag at me so?
Dialogue: 99,0:19:01.82,0:19:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Could it be?
Dialogue: 99,0:19:06.41,0:19:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps] A fire spell!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop burning,\Nplease stop burning!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:11.04,0:19:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] That was too close.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:14.67,0:19:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 99,0:19:17.38,0:19:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm starting\Nto get the hang of it.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:20.30,0:19:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bigger ones are more powerful\Nthan smaller ones.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:23.43,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And neatly drawn ones\Nlast longer than sloppy ones.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:27.14,0:19:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But drawing them that big\Nand that neat isn't easy.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:31.02,0:19:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Although he certainly\Nmade it look that way.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:34.06,0:19:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:35.32,0:19:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:19:40.15,0:19:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] I was right.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:41.57,0:19:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot easier to be neat
Dialogue: 99,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,when I trace the drawing\Nrather than copy it.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:54.46,0:19:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And done!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:19:59.26,0:20:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:20:15.31,0:20:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:20:16.57,0:20:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] What did you draw?
Dialogue: 99,0:20:18.02,0:20:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Coco!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:19.53,0:20:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What spell did you draw?
Dialogue: 99,0:20:21.11,0:20:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I don't know.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:22.74,0:20:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I traced a pattern\Nfrom the book, and I...
Dialogue: 99,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- [COCO'S MOM] Coco?\N- [Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Mom?
Dialogue: 99,0:20:33.54,0:20:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, run!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco's mom gasps, screams]
Dialogue: 99,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this isn't real.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[cries] Mom!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:48.22,0:20:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mom! Mom!\N- [QIFREY] Forbidden magic!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:50.97,0:20:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let go! I have to save my mom!\N- Hold still!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- She's in danger because of me!\N- I don't want to drop you!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:55.77,0:20:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] Stop it!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:56.94,0:20:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That spell is evil,\Nyou mustn't... No!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Coco cries]\N- [QIFREY] Coco!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:06.32,0:21:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] I'm here, Mom!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[wails] No!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:21:14.58,0:21:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[cries] I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:19.67,0:21:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] Of course you didn't.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:21.38,0:21:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all kept a secret\Nto prevent tragedies like this.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:25.18,0:21:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A special ink,\Nand a set of Casting Seals.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:28.97,0:21:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all one needs\Nfor magic to be used.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:31.89,0:21:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Concealing that is\Nour One Great Rule.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that\Nyou know the truth,
Dialogue: 99,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you must have\Nyour memories erased.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:39.86,0:21:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps, cries]
Dialogue: 99,0:21:43.03,0:21:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't! I can't forget.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:45.99,0:21:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do, then who'll save\Nmy mom?
Dialogue: 99,0:21:47.99,0:21:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I couldn't say.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:50.45,0:21:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know\Nwhat kind of magic it was,
Dialogue: 99,0:21:53.12,0:21:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can remember\Nall those drawings by heart!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:56.00,0:21:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And if all those memories\Nare lost, then my mom...
Dialogue: 99,0:21:59.13,0:22:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Qifrey gasps] The picture book.
Dialogue: 99,0:22:01.46,0:22:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 99,0:22:02.84,0:22:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If it came\Nfrom who I think it did,
Dialogue: 99,0:22:05.01,0:22:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,then I finally have a link\Nto their whereabouts!
Dialogue: 99,0:22:07.80,0:22:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl's memories\Nare my only chance
Dialogue: 99,0:22:10.01,0:22:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to track them down!
Dialogue: 99,0:22:11.81,0:22:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you remember\Nthe book by heart?
Dialogue: 99,0:22:14.18,0:22:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Hm.
Dialogue: 99,0:22:15.39,0:22:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] And you recall\Nthe page you copied?
Dialogue: 99,0:22:17.69,0:22:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Hmm.
Dialogue: 99,0:22:19.86,0:22:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] If we had\Nthe book I used,
Dialogue: 99,0:22:22.52,0:22:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I could show you\Nwhich seal I drew.
Dialogue: 99,0:22:26.32,0:22:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can find the one\Nthat hurt my Mom,
Dialogue: 99,0:22:28.91,0:22:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,do you think there's something\Nyou could do for her?
Dialogue: 99,0:22:33.87,0:22:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] There is a chance.
Dialogue: 99,0:22:37.87,0:22:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco cries] Mr. Qifrey,\Nplease don't erase my memories!
Dialogue: 99,0:22:41.67,0:22:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to do anything\Nto rescue my mother!
Dialogue: 99,0:22:47.38,0:22:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you keep our secret?
Dialogue: 99,0:22:49.26,0:22:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] I promise!
Dialogue: 99,0:22:51.93,0:22:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And are you willing to learn?
Dialogue: 99,0:22:53.72,0:22:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To learn... [gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:22:56.22,0:22:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] Once you know\Nthe truth, it cannot be undone.
Dialogue: 99,0:22:59.23,0:23:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, you must join\Nthose trusted with the secret.
Dialogue: 99,0:23:03.27,0:23:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That is your way forward,\Nthe only way.
Dialogue: 99,0:23:08.36,0:23:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Coco, from now on...\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:23:12.37,0:23:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be a witch.
